**Knowledgeable Wolf** | Werewolf Miscellaneous
__Basics__
The Knowledgeable Wolf starts out with some information about the role list.
__Details__
At the start of the game the Knowledgeable Wolf is told some of the roles on the role list.
The Hosts may also decide to tell the Knowledgeable Wolf about any game setup specific details.

__Simplified__
The Knowledgeable Wolf knows parts of the role list.

__Formalized__
Inherit: `Pack Lycan`
Starting: Learn `%PartialRoleList%`

__Card__
The Knowledgeable Wolf is well informed on who lives in the town.
